# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, refactor, test, chore, perf, ci
# Scope: api, frontend, agent-core, tools, skills, cron, alerts, db, auth
# Subject: imperative mood, no period, max 50 chars
#
# Examples:
#   feat(api): add Oracle AWR report generation tool
#   fix(frontend): resolve chat history loading race condition
#   refactor(agent-core): extract context budget into separate module
#   test(api): add integration tests for alert evaluation
